  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_supply_chain">NHS Supply Chain</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_supply_chain">NHS Supply Chain</xref>
 provides patient-focused healthcare products and supply chain services to the National Health Service (NHS).  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_supply_chain">NHS Supply Chain</xref>
 manages the sourcing, delivery and supply of healthcare products and food for 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_trust">NHS Trusts</xref>
 and 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Providers</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_supply_chain">NHS Supply Chain</xref>
, see the 
    <xref href="https://www.supplychain.nhs.uk/about-us/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">NHS Supply Chain website</xref>
.  </p>

